                <h2>Amsterdam</h2>
                <p>Amsterdam is the capital and most populated city of the Netherlands, with The Hague being the seat of government.  Amsterdam is considered an alpha world city by the Globalization and World Cities Research Network. Amsterdam's main attractions include its historic canals; the Rijksmuseum, the state museum with a vast collection of Dutch Golden Age art; the Van Gogh Museum and more!</p>
