                <h2>Paris</h2>
                <p>Paris is the capital and most populous city of France. Paris hosts several United Nations organizations including UNESCO, and other international organizations. Paris is especially known for its museums and architectural landmarks. The Musée d'Orsay, Musée Marmottan Monet and Musée de l'Orangerie are noted for their collections of French Impressionist art.</p>
