                <h2>Madrid</h2>
                <p>Madrid is the capital and most populous city of Spain. The Madrid urban agglomeration has the second-largest GDP in the European Union. While Madrid possesses modern infrastructure, it has preserved the look and feel of many of its historic neighbourhoods and streets. Its landmarks include the Plaza Mayor, the Royal Palace of Madrid; the Royal Theatre with its restored 1850 Opera House and even more!</p>
                <button type="button" onclick="moreInfoMadrid()">More info</button>
