                <h2>Sofia</h2>
                <p>Sofia is the capital and largest city of Bulgaria. Sofia is the 14th largest city in the European Union. With its cultural significance in Southeast Europe, Sofia is home to the National Opera and Ballet of Bulgaria, the National Palace of Culture, the Vasil Levski National Stadium, the Ivan Vazov National Theatre, the National Archaeological Museum, and the Serdica Amphitheatre.</p>
